msgid ""
"<strong>REST API</strong> - an API for settings, checkboxes, legal pages, "
"withdrawals and search."
msgstr ""
"<strong>REST API</strong> - eine API für Einstellungen, Kontrollkästchen, "
"rechtliche Seiten, Widerrufe und Suche."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Product badges</strong> - sale, new, featured and custom labels."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Produkt-Badges</strong> - Angebot, Neu, Empfohlen und eigene "
"Bezeichnungen."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid "<strong>AJAX search</strong> - live product search."
msgstr "<strong>AJAX-Suche</strong> - Live-Produktsuche."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid "<strong>Gallery zoom</strong> - enhanced product image zoom."
msgstr "<strong>Galerie-Zoom</strong> - verbesserter Zoom für Produktbilder."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid "<strong>Wishlist</strong> - save products for later."
msgstr "<strong>Wunschliste</strong> - Produkte für später speichern."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Delivery time</strong> - estimated delivery time on product pages "
"and product lists."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Lieferzeit</strong> - geschätzte Lieferzeit auf Produktseiten und in"
" Produktlisten."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Unit prices</strong> - price per kg, litre, metre, piece or a custom"
" unit."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Grundpreise</strong> - Preis pro kg, Liter, Meter, Stück oder eine "
"eigene Einheit."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>GPSR product fields</strong> - manufacturer, importer, EU "
"responsible person, product identifiers, safety warnings and instructions, "
"including CSV import and export."
msgstr ""
"<strong>GPSR-Produktfelder</strong> - Hersteller, Importeur, verantwortliche"
" Person in der EU, Produktkennungen, Sicherheitshinweise und Anleitungen, "
"einschließlich CSV-Import und -Export."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>HPOS compatible</strong> - supports WooCommerce High-Performance "
"Order Storage."
msgstr ""
"<strong>HPOS-kompatibel</strong> - unterstützt WooCommerce High-Performance "
"Order Storage."

#. Found in description list item.
msgid ""
"<strong>Modern code</strong> - PHP 8.1+, a React admin panel, REST API and "
"WP-CLI support."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Moderner Code</strong> - PHP 8.1+, ein React-Admin-Panel, REST API "
"und WP-CLI-Unterstützung."

